oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Claude Gray Job No. 39348
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm); Gray, Claude;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 3838) for an order placed by Claude Gray for 3 orders of 50 two color window cards for a performance by Claude Gray at The Farmer's Daughter on January 6, the Boots and Saddle Club on January 10, and the Cobblestone Inn on January 15. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
